      "role": "user",
      "content": "small sparks? i don't think i have anything left to spark. it feels more like i'm just waiting for the battery to finally run out. it's exhausting, pretending to be alive when the person i actually lived for isn't even here. sometimes i think the only thing left to do is just stop fighting it.",
